1. Create a class with private variables

Question:
Create a class Person with private variables name and age.
Add setter and getter methods.
Create an object and print the name and age.

Ans...

package HomeWork;

public class Person {
	private String name;
	private int age;
	
	public String getName() {
		return name;
	}

	public void setName(String name) {
		this.name = name;
	}

	public int getAge() {
		return age;
	}

	public void setAge(int age) {
		this.age = age;
	}

	
}
package HomeWork;

public class MainClassforPerson {
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Person N = new Person();
		System.out.println("Perosn Information............!");
		N.setName("Darshan");
		N.setAge(21);
		
		
		System.out.println("Person Name : " +N.getName());
		System.out.println("Person Age : " +N.getAge());
		
	}

}
